{"word":"λέμβος","slug":"λέμβος","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<entryFree id=\"n62366\" key=\"le/mbos\" type=\"main\" opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"entryFree\"> <orth extent=\"suff\" lang=\"greek\" opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"orth\">λέμβ-ος</orth>, <gen lang=\"greek\" opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"gen\">ὁ</gen>, a ship's <sense id=\"n62366.0\" n=\"A\" level=\"1\" opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"sense\"> <tr_ opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"tr\">cock-boat</tr_>, <bibl n=\"urn:cts:greekLit:tlg0014.tlg032.perseus-grc1:6\" default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <author TEIform=\"author\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ D.\">D.</a></author> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">32.6</biblScope> </bibl>: metaph., of a <tr_ opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"tr\">parasite</tr_>, <cit TEIform=\"cit\"> <quote_ lang=\"greek\" TEIform=\"quote\">ὄπισθεν ἀκολουθεῖ κόλαξ τῳ; λέμβος ἐπικέκληται</quote_> <bibl n=\"urn:cts:greekLit:tlg0405.tlg001:34:7\" default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <author TEIform=\"author\">Anaxandr.</author> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">34.7</biblScope></bibl></cit>. </sense> <sense n=\"II\" id=\"n62366.1\" level=\"2\" opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"sense\"> <tr_ opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"tr\">fishingboat</tr_>, <bibl n=\"urn:cts:greekLit:tlg0005.tlg001.perseus-grc1:21:12\" default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <author TEIform=\"author\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ Theoc.\">Theoc.</a></author> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">21.12</biblScope></bibl>. </sense> <sense n=\"2\" id=\"n62366.2\" level=\"3\" opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"sense\"> <tr_ opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"tr\">fast-sailing galley, felucca</tr_>, used either to precede a fleet, <bibl n=\"urn:cts:greekLit:tlg0543.tlg001.perseus-grc1:1:53:9\" default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <author TEIform=\"author\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ Plb.\">Plb.</a></author> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">1.53.9</biblScope> </bibl>; or as a light transport, <bibl n=\"urn:cts:greekLit:tlg0543.tlg001.perseus-grc1:2:3:1\" default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <author TEIform=\"author\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ Id.\">Id.</a></author> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">2.3.1</biblScope></bibl>, cf. <bibl n=\"urn:cts:greekLit:tlg0543.tlg001.perseus-grc1:5:109:3\" default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">5.109.3</biblScope></bibl>, <bibl default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <title_ TEIform=\"title\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ SIG\">SIG</a></title_> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">569.19</biblScope> </bibl> (Halasarna, <date TEIform=\"date\">iii B.C.</date>), <bibl n=\"http://www.trismegistos.org/text/78720\" default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <title_ TEIform=\"title\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ PPetr.\">PPetr.</a></title_> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">2p.64</biblScope> </bibl> <date TEIform=\"date\">(iii B.C.)</date>.</sense> </entryFree>"}]}